OL,3,CWhy Pep Guardiola's departure is sad
OL,4,Cfor all football fans not just Man City
OL,6,FOkay, so Manchester United, Liverpool
OL,7,Fand Arsenal supporters won't be
OL,8,Fshedding a tear after the official
OL,9,Fannouncement of Pep Guardiola's
OL,10,Fdeparture from Manchester City..
OL,12,FAfter all, the 55-year-old has
OL,13,Foverseen a decade of dominance for the
OL,14,Fclub, amassing an incredible 20
OL,15,Ftrophies including six Premier League
OL,16,Ftitles, a Champions League and a FIFA
OL,17,FClub World Cup.
OL,19,FBut Guardiola leaves with a legacy of
OL,20,Fmore than just trophies.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
