OL,3,CWhy Pep Guardiola's departure is sad
OL,4,Cfor all football fans not just Man City
OL,6,FTactically innovative with a drive for
OL,7,Fperfection, he's changed the way
OL,8,Ffootball is played in England and
OL,9,Finspired coaches throughout the league
OL,10,Fand beyond.
OL,12,FLike with all legendary managers,
OL,13,Fthink Sir Alex Ferguson at Manchester
OL,14,FUnited in 2013 and more recently
OL,15,FJurgen Klopp at Liverpool in 2024, the
OL,16,FPremier League is much poorer for Pep
OL,17,Fleaving.
OL,19,FHis departure has sparked a debate
OL,20,Fover who is better: Sir Alex or Pep?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
