OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779451870
OL,3,CWhy Pep Guardiola's departure is sad
OL,4,Cfor all football fans not just Man City
OL,6,FBut rather than pit one against the
OL,7,Fother, I'd rather celebrate the
OL,8,Fabsolute brilliance of both - supreme
OL,9,Fin their own way and their own time.
OL,11,FLove him or loathe him, Pep Guardiola
OL,12,Fdeparts not only as Manchester City's
OL,13,Fgreatest manager, but the greatest of
OL,14,Fhis generation and it's sad to see him
OL,15,Fgo.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
